                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3.5 w-3.5 text-forest-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                    <strong>Punto de salida:</strong> Cais da Rua dos Pescadores (muelle de pescadores), Caminha. El punto de llegada en España es Camposancos, no el terminal del ferry de A Guarda.
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3.5 w-3.5 text-forest-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
